Package SyntSpec

Class SSGenomeCarps

java.lang.Object
SyntSpec.SSCarps
SyntSpec.SSGenomeCarps
public class SSGenomeCarps extends SSCarps
SSGenomeCarps is a class that extends SSCarps with its own set genome, where a wild genome is one with all lowercase letters

      SSGenomeCarps constructor, with input genotype and input generation
      Parameters:
      newName - string identifier
      newAge - integer age in years
      length - length of the fish in cm
      newLocation - lake object where the fish lives
      bornLake - lake object where the fish was born
      dispersal - lake object for the fish's dispersal pattern
      ss - TRUE if the fish is sterile, else FALSE
      fgender - gender of the fish
      gt - genotype of the fish (can be anything?)
      gen - generation, used with GENE_GENERATION_DEATH. -1 if there should be no countdown to death
